{"tid":452622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[教局鳩噏洗腦]康乜鳩華: 中史用政治角度讀太heavy","createTime":"2017-10-30T11:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T23:19:25.000Z","uid":47359,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"36ebafd178f84dbf379bb862d6e36f1857ba6bb4","tid":452622,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母歷史唔講政治讀黎把撚呀？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1743940309047351&amp;id=715486135226112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1743940309047351%26id%3D715486135226112&d=VwsAVJ4%2Fp%2B1fcv%2Bs%2B2SN9ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=01b203d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1743940309047351&amp;id=715486135226112</a><br />\n<br />\n教育局就修訂初中中國歷史科課程，展開第二階段諮詢。教育局副秘書長康陳翠華表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">修訂不存在黑箱作業，又說將政治角度放落課程會很沉重，當局一直以專業角度修訂課程，讓學生有系統地了解國家歷史，有關洗腦教育的說法是不公允。</span><br />\n<br />\n她說，將來一定會有相關教科書，世界逃不過公理，到時可以看教科書，到底有甚麼內容是不可以接受。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #港台電視31 #港台電視32 #十點半新聞天地 #教育局 #中史 #陳翠華<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n個人簽名 &times;按此隱藏<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\nOct 28近期活躍五毛<br />\n0群龍共舞 1天才小釣手 2三色貓 3JR 4法國佬巫斯義 <br />\n5吾系甘開心牙 6真律師何君堯 7蘇麗珊 8十卜ching <br />\n9D_wade 10RedBaron 11優美開始 12阿古路 13Romanov <br />\n14返六日唔撚易 15優美開始 16民國復興 17dewi <br />\n18侵b 19曼聯明叔 20bb chu 21小翁翁</span>"},{"pid":"9ad5ea2abfd671a36231a5be6da6184f1313e32b","tid":452622,"uid":47359,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:46:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇就冇<br />\n乜撚野不存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"99b947711cdc5ba01eaab407c38136dd96c0b92d","tid":452622,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:46:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-